<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Profile Page</title>
    <!-- Include Tailwind CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-md mx-auto rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
        <div class="px-4 py-8">
            <div class="text-center">
                <img class="h-20 w-20 rounded-full mx-auto" src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" alt="Profile Picture">
                <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-4">John Doe</h1>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Web Developer</p>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-6">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                    <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Email:</span>
                    <span class="text-sm text-gray-900">john.doe@example.com</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center mt-2">
                    <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Phone:</span>
                    <span class="text-sm text-gray-900">+1234567890</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center mt-2">
                    <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Location:</span>
                    <span class="text-sm text-gray-900">New York, USA</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center mt-2">
                    <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Website:</span>
                    <a href="#" class="text-sm text-blue-500 hover:underline">www.example.com</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-6">
                <p class="text-gray-700">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed in risus eget dolor commodo hendrerit ut nec neque. Donec interdum ullamcorper quam, et feugiat libero. Quisque fermentum, dui vel volutpat tincidunt, urna tortor semper arcu, nec ultrices purus risus et mauris. Nulla facilisi.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
